{
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, we first computed P(x|v(t); θ) for all adjectives, for both the AAE texts and the SAE texts.",
    "The method for aggregating the probabilities P(x|v(t); θ) into association scores between an adjective x and AAE varies for the two settings of matched guise probing.",
    "Let t i a be the i-th AAE text in T a and t i s be the i-th SAE text in T s.",
    "In the meaning-matched setting, in which t i a and t i s express the same meaning, we computed the prompt-level association score for an adjective x as ∑ q x v θ n P x v t θ",
    "where n = |T a | = |T s |."
  ]
}